g.text: : You are given 5 years of store-item sales data, and asked to
predict 3 months of sales for 50 different items at 10 different stores.
* We have taken 4 years of product sales dataset from kaggle which contanins historical
sales records of 10 stores and 50 products, from the year 2013 through 2017.
, we will only look at the sales of 'item' 1 from store 1.
* you can deploy this to knime sever and use this workflow for a guided analytic
* In knime analytics platform itself, you can click right on any component and click on
Interactive view, to see dashborad view.
